node.text:
⭐ SAVE 20% off @naturaldogcompany with code INSTAHUSKY at NaturalDog.com ▪️ worldwide shipping ▪️ ad 📷: @wolfmans.brother
.
Every adventure should start with #Pawtection! Harsh surfaces like hot pavement, sand, salt, ice and snow can really take a toll on dog paws. By applying #Pawtection before heading out, you’re adding an all-natural layer of protection, helping to prevent drying and lock in moisture. It’s 100% natural and safe!
